items.name: Arnas Atakiyo ( CappyAdams' OG Character/OC)
items.description:
6 years ago, I made this dude in my mind and I loved him since. I was changing his design, giving him new outfits, made 3D models of him, etc and now it's time to make him into a LoRA! I mostly made this LoRA to experiment with AI... but it's honestly a pretty good model if ya use it correctly and if ya do enough experimenting. anyways, here's some info and stuff

RECOMMENDATIONS (V1.1)!

  • Sampling Method: DPM++ 2M Karras OR DPM++ SDE Karras

  • Resolution: 512 x 512 (or lower)

RECOMMENDED!:

  • I HIGHLY recommend using EnvyBetterHands and EasyNegative

  • Lora weight = 0.5 - 1

  • I recommend using Anime-ish checkpoints (Anything V5/Ink is a good one!)

  • You can tick the "Restore Faces" box if you're having issues with the face

NOTES!:

  • putting "Masterpiece, Best Quality, best quality face, beautiful eyes" in the prompt should help with generating better images

  • This LoRA is an EXPERIMENT and is.... not the best with full body images. It's okay with Cowboy shots tho. At the moment it's the best with Upper body and Close-up images (especially with close-ups)

  • The character has multiple outfits and in the detaset there are multiple images with multiple outfits. to get his main outfit, put "black hoodie, black pants, black shoes" in the prompt.

  • IMPAINTING THE FACE IS OFTEN NEEDED

RECOMMENDED TAGS!:

Main tag/keyword: ArnasAtakiyo

NEGATIVE PROMPT: (low quality, worst quality:1.4), lowres, bad anatomy, bad hands, four hands, four legs, two people, cut image, censored, author name, water marks, web address, artist name, multicolored hair, blurred face, bad face, heart, blue heart, (easynegative:0.1), 1girl, gloves, extra fingers,

(Feel free to add more tags to the negative prompt... or remove some tags..)

also, sometimes ya might need to add "colored tongue, blue tongue" the postive prompt

WARNING!:

This model MIGHT ACCIDENTLY generate nsfw/graphic content. This has never happened to me, however I still wanted to make this small disclaimer since I don't want anyone complaining. to prevent this, put nsfw tags and the "injury" tag in the negative prompt

EXTRA INFO!:

  • Trained on 46 images of the character/3D model

CONTACT INFO:

Twitter: YuriMayori

DeviantArt: CappyAdams

A Website of Mine: (This link)

Giant concrete creations bearing the imprint of rain wash, as if the traces of time, can somehow always give people a spiritual impact. This model is also out of this kind of nostalgic purpose, trying to make the architectural model not only limited to the modern, ancient or science fiction themes, but also another choice.

items.name: Samantha Fox (1985-89 era - CHECKPOINT)
items.description:
THERE IS A LORA VERSION OF THIS MODEL AVAILABLE.

Shivam Dreambooth of British 1980s glamor model Samantha Fox, using 77 ref images and 1980 (real) reg images, for 12,000 steps. The period covered is around 1985-1989.

I generally use these models in complex workflows, inpainting faces after initial T2Is, and using ControlNet extensively. So if you're hoping for one-click prompt magic, my models aren't data-curated with this in mind, but rather as tools for traditional workflows that use Photoshop and other older methods.

Due to the nature of the only source material available, this model will almost certainly produce subject-accurate NSFW output unless countered in negative prompts.

LoRA inspired by the style of the artist Tony Taka. Follow and support the artist if you like their work.

items.name: Futura Holly
items.description:
My rating vs expectation: 96%

(High quality dataset. Very happy with likeness here. See "about this version" to see changes, and TIPS to get best result. This is the final version for Holly.)

All TIs I make depict real adults. Please apply it with good judgement. If you're the model and want this removed reach out to me via link below. I welcome all criticisms and suggestions with curiosity. If you like my work, buy me a house:
https://ko-fi.com/futurafree

This TI was trained in sd1.5 base with 5 vectors, 25 images, 12500 steps, and 500 epochs. This was finetuned for epiCRealism evo3 and Realistic Vision V4.0, but may work on others.

TIPS:

  • MUST be the first word in the prompt for likeness and consistency.

    • Example: futuraholly12500v52, portrait of a woman, long dress etc.

    • Not: Portrait of futuraholly12500v52, etc.

  • Recommended strength:

    • (0.98-1.0)

  • I use adetailer for all images, with mediapipe_face_full, blank pos and neg, 1024x1024, inpaint mask blur: 20, inpaint noise strength: 0.45.

  • Again, prompt in adetailer is left blank most of the time; (*exception*: if Loras/Lycoris is used and has significant impact on the appearance of the model's face, copy paste pos prompt without Loras/Lycoris into adetailer).

  • Upscaler I use: 4x_NMKD-Siax_200k.

items.description:
Original character - Rena Aikawa

Rena Aikawa is an 18-year-old girl with a striking appearance that turns heads wherever she goes. With her short blonde hair, captivating green eyes, and dark skin, she exudes a unique and alluring charm. Her figure is the envy of many, featuring large breasts, wide hips, long legs, and a round, firm butt that adds to her natural allure.

Currently living in her own apartment, Rena is a dedicated student of communications. She aspires to use her skills to connect with people and make a positive impact on the world. Beyond her academic pursuits, Rena has a dynamic personality that keeps her life thrilling and unpredictable.

Her interests span a wide range of activities. She loves running outside, feeling the wind in her hair as she embraces the freedom and adventure it brings. Rena has a penchant for fighting too, a somewhat unexpected passion that often leads her into confrontations, driven by her hot-headed nature.

In contrast to her bold and daring side, Rena has a soft spot for the arts. Drawing is one of her creative outlets, allowing her to express her emotions and imagination on paper. But beneath her sweet exterior, Rena has a hidden kinky side. She's open about her sexuality and embraces her desires, often engaging in intimate encounters to satiate her sexual urges.

What nobody knows is that Rena is not just an ordinary girl. In secret, she is an angel from another dimension, sent on a special mission to observe and understand human emotions and connections. This unique perspective gives her a deeper insight into the world around her, making her interactions with people even more meaningful.

When it comes to her attire, Rena has a few signature outfits. For casual days, she likes to wear a white long-sleeved shirt paired with a short black pleated skirt, accentuating her youthful and stylish vibe. In more intimate moments, she feels confident and comfortable in a white bra and short black boyshorts.

With her vibrant personality, captivating looks, and hidden celestial origin, Rena Aikawa leads a life full of adventure, connection, and self-discovery. Her journey is one of both physical and emotional exploration, seeking to find her place in both the human world and the realm of angels.

  • Trained with anime (full-final-pruned) model, using artworks drawn by me and some generated with waifulabs.com.

  • 3 versions; 10, 8, and 7 epochs.

  • Works the best with ALL, MIDD, OUTD, and OUTALL LoRA weight blocks, but I highly recommend you OUTALL to get smoother results.

  • Recommended LoRA weights: 0.7+

  • Activation tags: aikawa rena to get the character's overall info, and rena underwear to get her underwear.

    • rena underwear; use "[rena underwear:(white ribbon:1.4):1.3]" with "(boyshorts, black shorts:1.2), (white bra:1.3)" to get the underwear I designed for her. Place all these in the Negative prompt box to get other clothing.

  • If the resulting images end being messy, try any of the following:

    • Use OUTD or OUTALL LoRA weight blocks, instead.

    • Place tags of those things you don't want in the "Negative prompt" text box.

    • Lower the weight of the LoRA.

    • Don't the use the LoRA in txt2img, but in img2img to alter that initial image.

    • Lower the weights of the activation tags.

    • In txt2img; if the mistakes occur with "10 epochs", use "8 epochs" or "7 epochs", instead.

THERE IS A LORA VERSION OF THIS MODEL AVAILABLE. IT IS EXACTLY THE SAME MODEL AS THIS ONE, EXCEPT IN A DIFFERENT AND LIGHTER FORMAT.

Shivam Dreambooth of American Taxi and Evening Shade actress Marilu Henner, using 77 ref images and 1400 (real) reg images, for 8,000 steps. The period covered is around 1978-83.

This model was trained on unusually high-quality data, though mainly of posed publicity stills. Therefore it may prove repetitive in a text-to-image context, but is well-suited for high quality image-to-image work.

No nudes were in the training data, so while the model may sometimes produce some racy images, it is not likely to produce truly NSFW output by default.

I generally use these models in complex workflows, inpainting faces after initial T2Is, and using ControlNet extensively. So if you're hoping for one-click prompt magic, my models aren't data-curated with this in mind, but rather as tools for traditional workflows that use Photoshop and other older methods.

items.description:
If you enjoyed this model, why don't you check out my other works? I put a lot of effort into correctly recreating artist styles and making the occasional character LoRA.😊

This model was trained using the collab/guide by holostrawberry [Guide] Make your own Loras, easy and free - colabs | Stable Diffusion Other | Civitai

I noticed that we have multiple Shuten Douji LoRA but Ibaraki doesn't get any love. Furthermore I wanted to see how well you can include multiple versions without creating specific prompts and I've gotta say, I prefer it this way.

Because fanart is limited for some of her versions, I recommend experimenting with the later prompts, especially with prompts changing the hair color.

Weights & Prompts

This version is pretty strong overall. I recommend a weight of 0.7-1.0.

At around 0.7 the clothes become less accurate, below 0.6 the hands are less likely to be red and below 0.4 you lose most other details (check out the XYZ plot for details).

The only necessary prompt is:

ibaraki_douji

It is the titular main antagonist in Stephen King's 1986 horror novel It. The character is an ancient, trans-dimensional evil entity who preys upon the children (and sometimes adults) of Derry, Maine, roughly every 27 years, using a variety of powers that include the ability to shapeshift, manipulate reality, and go unnoticed by adults. During the course of the story, It primarily appears in the form of Pennywise the Dancing Clown.

King stated in a 2013 interview that he came up with the idea for Pennywise after asking himself what children feared "more than anything else in the world", and feeling that the answer was clowns.King thought of a troll like the one in the children's tale "Three Billy Goats Gruff",though he imagined it living in a sewer system rather than under a bridge.

The character was portrayed in its Pennywise form by Tim Curry in the 1990 television adaptation and by Bill Skarsgård in the 2017 film adaptation and its 2019 sequel It Chapter Two.
